snippet.title: Lil Gator Game: In The Dark | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Lil Gator is back! A whole new adventure awaits IN THE DARK! Join Lil Gator underground and embark on a new adventure, with new toys and new stories to be made!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1586800/Lil_Gator_Game/

In The Dark is a new, game-sized DLC in the works for Lil Gator Game! Stay tuned for more info soon!
